div class=\"elementor-field\" id=\"form-field-field_44e5818\"><div class=\"elementor-g-recaptcha\" data-sitekey=\"6LdtFHIhAAAAAENXS8JO7-KljjwNvLYnJjJRb5gX\" data-type=\"v3\" data-action=\"Form\" data-badge=\"inline\" data-size=\"invisible\"><\/div><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-field-group elementor-column elementor-field-type-submit elementor-col-100 e-form__buttons\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<button class=\"elementor-button elementor-size-sm\" type=\"submit\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-content-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-text\">Send<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/button>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/form>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-0d5fd30 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"0d5fd30\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-6844da2\" data-id=\"6844da2\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-58c1e87 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"58c1e87\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-large\">Habitat, Behavior, Lifecycle<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-59effcd elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"59effcd\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>The American cockroach is a common household pest in Canada, often in warm and moist environments. It is one of the largest cockroach species and is known for its brownish-red color and distinctive yellowish markings on its head.<\/p><p><strong>Habitat: <\/strong>The American cockroach is found in many habitats, including homes, restaurants, grocery stores, hospitals, and other commercial buildings. In Canada, they tend to thrive in warm and humid environments, such as basements, crawl spaces, and other damp areas. They are also attracted to food sources and can be found in kitchens, pantries, and garbage areas. American cockroaches can enter buildings through cracks and gaps in windows, doors, and walls and can also be transported in infested items such as boxes, furniture, and appliances.<\/p><p><strong>Behavior: <\/strong>American cockroaches are nocturnal insects and are most active at night. They are omnivorous and will feed on various foods, including garbage, decaying organic matter, and other insects. They are also attracted to starchy and sugary foods like cereal, bread, and sweets. American cockroaches are known for their ability to fly short distances, which they use to escape danger or to search for food and mates.<\/p><p><strong>Lifecycle: <\/strong>The American cockroach has a relatively long lifecycle, taking up to 15 months to develop from an egg to an adult. The female American cockroach can produce up to 150 eggs in her lifetime, which she deposits in an ootheca protective capsule. The eggs hatch into nymphs, which go through several molts before reaching adulthood. The entire lifecycle of the American cockroach takes place in warm and moist environments, where the nymphs can find the food and shelter they need to develop.<\/p><p>Combat the trio of American cockroaches,\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/acmepestsolutions.com\/wood-cockroaches\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><u><b>wood cockroaches<\/b><\/u><\/a>, and\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/acmepestsolutions.com\/smoky-brown-cockroaches\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><u><b>smoky brown cockroaches<\/b><\/u><\/a>\u00a0with our expert pest control strategies to ensure a cockroach-free and healthy living space.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-548fe4a elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"548fe4a\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-large\">How do American cockroaches spread?<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-90a8333 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"90a8333\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>American cockroaches are among the most common pests found in homes and buildings. These insects can easily spread from one location to another, making them a nuisance for homeowners and business owners. One of the primary ways that American cockroaches spread is through their ability to fly. These insects have wings that allow them to move quickly and easily from one location to another, often traveling several blocks searching for food, shelter or water.<\/p><p>In addition to flying, American cockroaches can also crawl into small spaces and crevices, making it easy to enter homes and buildings undetected. Once inside a building, they can quickly reproduce and establish new colonies. This makes it challenging for property owners to control these pests without professional assistance.<\/p><p>Finally, American cockroaches are known for their resilience and adaptability. They can survive extreme temperatures, harsh environments and even chemical treatments designed to eliminate them. This allows them to continue spreading from one location to another regardless of attempts made by property owners or pest control companies. As such, it is important for individuals dealing with an infestation of American cockroaches to seek out professional help as soon as possible to prevent the further spread of these resilient pests.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-9ce42ef elementor-section-full_width elementor-section-stretched elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"9ce42ef\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;stretch_section&quot;:&quot;section-stretched&quot;,&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-33 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-b3b038b\" data-id=\"b3b038b\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-33 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-9117bb7\" data-id=\"9117bb7\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-9846d57 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"9846d57\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Residential Pest Control Service<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5d9eaca elementor-widget e